FeedEntry.create(:id => 466, :name => "The “being realistic” fallacy", :summary => "<a href=\"http://leostartsup.com/2012/12/the-%e2%80%9cbeing-realistic%e2%80%9d-fallacy/\" class=\"excerpt_thumb_link\" title=\" \" ><img src=\"http://leostartsup.com/wp-content/plugins/superslider-excerpt/plugin-data/superslider/ssExcerpt/excerpt-thumbs/cat-uncategorized.jpg\"  width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"excerpt_thumb  cat-uncategorized \" alt=\"excerpt thumb\" /></a><p>On my way to the airport this week, I’ve had an amazing conversation with Joel. It was about a topic I thought I had nailed for a long time and realized that actually rather the opposite was the case. Joel (&hellip;)</p><p><a href=\"http://leostartsup.com/2012/12/the-%e2%80%9cbeing-realistic%e2%80%9d-fallacy/\">Read the rest of this entry &raquo;</a></p></p>", :url => "http://leostartsup.com/2012/12/the-%e2%80%9cbeing-realistic%e2%80%9d-fallacy/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-%25e2%2580%259cbeing-realistic%25e2%2580%259d-fallacy", :published_at => Sat, 29 Dec 2012 18:10:24 UTC +00:00, :guid => "http://leostartsup.com/?p=548", :feed_title => "Leo Widrich", :feed_id => 13)
FeedEntry.create(:id => 467, :name => "Why I dropped out of college to work on a startup", :summary => "<a href=\"http://leostartsup.com/2012/12/why-i-dropped-out-of-college-to-work-on-a-startup/\" class=\"excerpt_thumb_link\" title=\" \" ><img src=\"http://leostartsup.com/wp-content/plugins/superslider-excerpt/plugin-data/superslider/ssExcerpt/excerpt-thumbs/cat-uncategorized.jpg\"  width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"excerpt_thumb  cat-uncategorized \" alt=\"excerpt thumb\" /></a><p>On this day, around 2 years ago, I’m about a few weeks away before I’ve had a brief Skype chat with Joel on a side project he was working on. He’d called it bfffr.com. It was a site that would (&hellip;)</p><p><a href=\"http://leostartsup.com/2012/12/why-i-dropped-out-of-college-to-work-on-a-startup/\">Read the rest of this entry &raquo;</a></p></p>", :url => "http://leostartsup.com/2012/12/why-i-dropped-out-of-college-to-work-on-a-startup/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=why-i-dropped-out-of-college-to-work-on-a-startup", :published_at => Sat, 22 Dec 2012 18:00:50 UTC +00:00, :guid => "http://leostartsup.com/?p=545", :feed_title => "Leo Widrich", :feed_id => 13)
